{"tid":38380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【咁狠】告白男心形蠟燭陣等女神 阿Sir滅火筒狂噴","createTime":"2016-12-14T01:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T03:59:15.000Z","uid":18348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61a86a7baaee2351b92de7c104f5de27931000c9","tid":38380,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161214/large/1481676144_a055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161214%2Flarge%2F1481676144_a055.jpg&h=f249794f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時候告白失敗，不一定因為被女神拒絕，還有可能是因為學校老師的滅火筒！<br />\n<br />\n河南鄭州財經學院一名男生，前日在校內擺了一個心形蠟燭陣，打算向女神告白，未料女神還沒現身，老師就拿着滅火筒，來勢洶洶地將點燃的蠟燭全部撲滅！一場還未開始的告白就這樣無疾而終，而在旁圍觀的「花生友」也驚呆了！<br />\n<br />\n秒拍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161214/56044216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161214%2F56044216&d=kPeyU4V5V1v7Aiz%2F0ok8NEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3ddcfcb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20161214%2F56044216&h=350ea9c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20161214/56044216</a>"},{"pid":"b7be0601e80fadf4fabef8ba5d4ae428f311401d","tid":38380,"uid":4162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593843ae35bcce162f7ce15e30b3097e2da13322","tid":38380,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能佢女神叫阿sir咁做"},{"pid":"1dc9b77ec32f1ce8db4375fb511b6da5c0a137df","tid":38380,"uid":30562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"打壓校員戀愛<img src=\"/assets/fac